    "id": "component:page-constructor:button:props",
    "section_title": "Props",
    "content": "Props for Button:\n\n- analyticsEvents: AnalyticsEventsBase — Analytics events to track\n- className: string — Additional CSS class\n- id: string — HTML id attribute\n- img: object | string — Button icon. If string, specify the icon link. If object, specify url, position, alt\n- onClick: React.MouseEventHandler<HTMLButtonElement | HTMLAnchorElement> — Click handler\n- size: 'xs' | 's' | 'ns' | 'n' | 'm' | 'l' | 'head' | 'promo' — default: l — Button size\n- text: string — Button text\n- theme: 'action' | 'clear' | 'link' | 'normal' | 'pseudo' | 'raised' | 'github' | 'app-store' | 'google-play' | 'scale' | 'monochrome' — default: normal — Button look and feel\n- url: string — Button link URL\n- urlTitle: string — Button URL title attribute\n- width: string — Button width"
  },
