    "section_title": "Props",
    "content": "Props for Map:\n\n- address: string — URL-escaped place name, address. Required for Google Maps\n- areaMargin: number | [number, number] | [number, number, number] — default: 30 — Offset (in pixels) for the marked area of the map. Only for Yandex Maps\n- copyrightPosition: {top?: number; right?: number; bottom?: number; left?: number} — Position of the copyright text. Only for Yandex Maps\n- disableBalloons: boolean — default: false — If true, disables info balloon opening when clicking on a marker. Only for Yandex Maps\n- disableControls: boolean — default: false — If true, hides map's default controls. Only for Yandex Maps\n- forceAspectRatio: boolean — default: true — Determines whether map's aspect ratio is forced automatically (16:9 for Desktop, 4:3 for Mobile)\n- id: string — Map id. Required for Yandex Maps\n- markers: object[] — Description for placemarkers. Required for Yandex Maps\n- zoom: number — Map zoom level"
  },
